   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-2",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from kaggle_environments import make\n",
    "\n",
    "env = make(\"orbit_wars\", debug=True)\n",
    "print(f\"环境: {env.name} v{env.version}\")\n",
    "print(f\"玩家: {env.specification.agents}\")\n",
    "print(f\"最大步数: {env.configuration.episodeSteps}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-3",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 理解观测数据\n",
    "\n",
    "每回合你的智能体接收到的观测数据包含：\n",
    "- `player` - 你的玩家 ID（0-3）\n",
    "- `planets` - 列表，元素为 `[id, owner, x, y, radius, ships, production]`\n",
    "- `fleets` - 列表，元素为 `[id, owner, x, y, angle, from_planet_id, ships]`\n",
    "- `angular_velocity` - 内圈行星的旋转速度（弧度/回合）\n",
    "\n",
    "你的智能体返回一个行动列表：`[from_planet_id, angle_in_radians, num_ships]`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-4",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 运行一局快速游戏，看看观测数据长什么样\n",
    "env = make(\"orbit_wars\", debug=True)\n",
    "env.run([\"random\", \"random\"])\n",
    "\n",
    "# 查看初始观测\n",
    "from kaggle_environments.envs.orbit_wars.orbit_wars import Planet, Fleet\n",
    "\n",
    "obs = env.steps[1][0].observation  # step 1 = 第一个行动步\n",
    "planets = [Planet(*p) for p in obs.planets]\n",
    "print(f\"玩家: {obs.player}\")\n",
    "print(f\"角速度: {obs.angular_velocity:.4f} 弧度/回合\")\n",
    "print(f\"\\n行星 ({len(planets)} 个):\")\n",
    "for p in planets[:6]:\n",
    "    owner_str = f\"Player {p.owner}\" if p.owner >= 0 else \"中立\"\n",
    "    print(f\"  id={p.id} owner={owner_str:10s} pos=({p.x:.1f}, {p.y:.1f}) r={p.radius:.1f} ships={p.ships} prod={p.production}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-5",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 智能体 1：最近行星狙击手\n",
    "\n",
    "我们的第一个智能体使用一个简单的策略：\n",
    "1. 对于我们拥有的每个行星，找到最近的**不归我们所有**的行星\n",
    "2. 检查我们是否有足够的舰船来占领它（需要比目标的驻军更多）\n",
    "3. 发送刚好足够的舰船来夺取它（目标舰船数 + 1）\n",
    "\n",
    "这教会了基本要素：读取观测数据、计算角度和发送舰队。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-6",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import math\n",
    "from kaggle_environments.envs.orbit_wars.orbit_wars import Planet\n",
    "\n",
    "def nearest_planet_sniper(obs):\n",
    "    moves = []\n",
    "    player = obs.get(\"player\", 0) if isinstance(obs, dict) else obs.player\n",
    "    raw_planets = obs.get(\"planets\", []) if isinstance(obs, dict) else obs.planets\n",
    "    planets = [Planet(*p) for p in raw_planets]\n",
    "\n",
    "    # 区分我方行星和敌方目标\n",
    "    my_planets = [p for p in planets if p.owner == player]\n",
    "    targets = [p for p in planets if p.owner != player]\n",
    "\n",
    "    if not targets:\n",
    "        return moves\n",
    "\n",
    "    for mine in my_planets:\n",
    "        # 找到最近的不归我们所有的行星\n",
    "        nearest = None\n",
    "        min_dist = float('inf')\n",
    "        for t in targets:\n",
    "            dist = math.sqrt((mine.x - t.x)**2 + (mine.y - t.y)**2)\n",
    "            if dist < min_dist:\n",
    "                min_dist = dist\n",
    "                nearest = t\n",
    "\n",
    "        if nearest is None:\n",
    "            continue\n",
    "\n",
    "        # 我们需要多少舰船？目标驻军 + 1\n",
    "        ships_needed = max(nearest.ships + 1, 20)\n",
    "\n",
    "        # 只有当我们有足够舰船时才发送\n",
    "        if mine.ships >= ships_needed:\n",
    "            # 计算从我方行星到目标的角度\n",
    "            angle = math.atan2(nearest.y - mine.y, nearest.x - mine.x)\n",
    "            moves.append([mine.id, angle, ships_needed])\n",
    "\n",
    "    return moves"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-7",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 用随机智能体测试我们的智能体\n",
    "env = make(\"orbit_wars\", debug=True)\n",
    "env.run([nearest_planet_sniper, \"random\"])\n",
    "\n",
    "final = env.steps[-1]\n",
    "for i, s in enumerate(final):\n",
    "    print(f\"玩家 {i}: reward={s.reward}, status={s.status}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "env.render(mode=\"ipython\", width=800, height=600)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-8",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 这个智能体有什么问题？\n",
    "\n",
    "狙击手智能体有几个问题：\n",
    "- 它没有考虑**旅行时间**——目标行星在舰队飞行途中仍在生产舰船\n",
    "- 它从**每个**行星都发送舰队，即使多个行星瞄准同一个目标\n",
    "- 它忽略了**太阳**——穿过中心的舰队会被摧毁\n",
    "- 它将舰船留在没有附近目标的行星上，而不是进行集结整合\n",
    "\n",
    "让我们在 4 人游戏中试试，看看它的表现如何："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "cell-9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "env4 = make(\"orbit_wars\", debug=True)\n",
    "env4.run([nearest_planet_sniper, nearest_planet_sniper, nearest_planet_sniper, nearest_planet_sniper])\n",
    "\n",
    "final = env4.steps[-1]\n",
    "for i, s in enumerate(final):\n",
    "    print(f\"玩家 {i}: reward={s.reward}, status={s.status}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "env4.render(mode=\"ipython\", width=800, height=600)"
   ]
  },
